title: "AgentOS Frameworks in 2026: A Comparative Evaluation for Personal-Scale Knowledge Work"
version: "4.0"
date-released: 2026-03-14
url: "https://github.com/havmeaning/personal-ai-operating-system"
repository-code: "https://github.com/havmeaning/personal-ai-operating-system"
license: MIT
abstract: >
  A structured comparative evaluation of seven AgentOS frameworks available in March 2026,
  assessed across maturity, philosophy, knowledge management, orchestration, privacy,
  regulatory alignment (EU AI Act), and suitability for individual knowledge workers.
  The PAIOS modular hybrid emerges as the sole immediately deployable solution combining
  productivity gains with high privacy and EU AI Act readiness.
keywords:
